"{\"uid\": \"lbc.co.uk-article-five-time-olympic-medallist-tom-daley-announces-his-retirement-from-diving-5HjcpRZ_2\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"By Asher McShane  Five-time Olympic medallist Tom Daley has announced his retirement from diving.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 97, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 46, \"end\": 55, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 4.554937629643169e-48, \"text\": \"Tom Daley\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Tom_Daley\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He announced his retirement in an interview with British Vogue magazine after returning from Paris.\", \"from\": 99, \"to\": 198, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 148, \"end\": 161, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.621740604483677e-30, \"text\": \"British Vogue\", \"types\": [\"Q41298\", \"Q386724\", \"Q234460\", \"Q1092563\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Vogue\"}, {\"begin\": 192, \"end\": 197, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999992010089, \"rank\": 7.988028482124261e-10, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cIt was emotional at the end, up there on the platform, knowing it was going to be my last competitive dive,\\\" he said.\", \"from\": 200, \"to\": 320, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But I have to make the decision at some point, and it feels like the right time.\", \"from\": 322, \"to\": 403, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"It\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s the right time to call it a day.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d  Daley brought home a silver medal in this year's 10\\u00c2\\u00a0metre synchronised diving.\", \"from\": 404, \"to\": 527, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\"